## KGC Machafi (Production) — API hardening

Options -Indexes

<IfModule mod_headers.c>
  Header always set X-Content-Type-Options "nosniff"
  Header always set X-Frame-Options "SAMEORIGIN"
  Header always set Cache-Control "no-store, no-cache, must-revalidate, max-age=0"
</IfModule>

# Prevent direct access to config files if placed in web root (recommended: keep config above web root)
<FilesMatch "^(admin-config\.php|\.env|composer\.(json|lock)|package(-lock)?\.json)$">
  Require all denied
</FilesMatch>

